            <tr class="border-t border-border-light"><th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-text-dark">Best for</th><td class="p-4 text-text-mid">Dynamic / variable loads</td><td class="p-4 text-text-mid">Stable, predictable loads</td></tr>
